  <title>Manage roles</title>

  <para>A role contains a number of permissions such as access to an application or the right to modify the project. 
  NovaForge allows the project manager to create its own roles and the correspondence between these roles and the roles of tools available.</para>

  <sect2>
    <title>Create a role</title>
     <sect3>
     <title>Under the forge project </title>
     <para>In section <emphasis
    role="bold">«Project administration/Your memberships/Your roles/Create a role»</emphasis>, you can create a role.</para>
     
    
       
     </sect3>
     <sect3>
     <title>Under a specific project</title>
     <para>In section <emphasis
    role="bold">«Project administration/Your memberships/Your roles/Create a role»</emphasis>, you can create a role and optionally can be linked to an application role.</para>
      
     </sect3>
     
 </sect2>
     
     <para>Once the role is created it can be changed : <emphasis
    role="bold">«Edit the role information»</emphasis> of column <emphasis role="bold">«ACTIONS»</emphasis>.</para>
     
     
  
</sect1>